For completeness, you can also add a **verification schedule** and **audit fields** to the crisis resource dataset so compliance or safety staff can document updates regularly. Example keys:

```json
{
  "audit": {
    "next_review_due": "2024-09-01",
    "review_interval_days": 90,
    "contact_person": "SafetyOpsTeam",
    "change_history": [
      {"date": "2024-06-01", "changes": "added Canada/FR resource"},
      {"date": "2024-03-01", "changes": "re‑verified UK Samaritan number"}
    ]
  }
}
```

These meta‑fields make it easier to prove that hotline data stay current and accurate — a common requirement for ethical conversational systems.  

